		<lb n="1"/>[teṉṉa]var mūvaruḷ
		va ••• iruvarukka<lb n="2" break="no"/>[ru]ḷi-k kāṉakam
		Oruvaṉukkaḷittu-p porucilai <lb n="3"/>[ci]rccilaic ceralaṉ
		velaikeḻu kāntaḷūr[cā]<lb n="4" break="no"/>lai kalamaṟuppitt'
