		muṭitta<lb n="7" break="no"/>lai taṭintu taṉ koṭippaṭ[ai] yevi-k
		ka<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṉṉāṭakar viṭu kaṭakari puraḷat
		taṉṉāṭaiyi<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṟ tamiḻpparaṇikoṇ ṭoṉṉār
		vacci[ra]<lb n="10" break="no"/>neṭuvāḷ vicciyaṉ veruneḷitt'
		añ[ci]<lb n="11" break="no"/>yoṭi vañciyampaṭaiyāl
		āṅkavaṉ [pi]<lb n="12" break="no"/>tāvai mātāvoṭum catāmali
		viṅku nirppū<lb n="13" break="no"/>ṇṭura veñcamattakappa[ṭu]tt'
		am(p)paṭai <lb n="14"/>āhavamallaṉ payattoṭum
		varaviṭum O<lb n="15"/>ṟṟarai veru[va]rappiṭippitt'
		āṅkavar mā<hi rend="grantha">[na]</hi><lb n="16" break="no"/>vil āhavamallaṉ
		yāṅṅaṇam aiñci<lb n="17" break="no"/>ṉaneṉṉa naṉkeḻutic
		celuttiya [pi]ṉ<lb n="18" break="no"/>taṉ pulikkoṭip paṭaiñar
		oṭṭalari vāraṇa
	</p>
	
